  "explanation": "The defendant is a first-time offender who committed a non-violent financial crime and has demonstrated remorse by making partial restitution. While embezzlement is a serious breach of trust, the requested 10-year term from a spectator is excessive and legally disproportionate to the amount stolen. A sentence of 8 months is sufficient to serve as a punitive measure and a deterrent, while allowing for the possibility of rehabilitation.",
